HEADWORD: Familiarization
<hw>Fa*mil`iar*i*za"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act
or process of making familiar; the result of becoming familiar; <as>as,
<ex>familiarization</ex> with scenes of blood</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

